601
00:49:39.893 --> 00:49:41.185
The name's Scaramanga.

602
00:49:41.269 --> 00:49:42.895
Mr. Fat is
expecting me.

603
00:50:05.460 --> 00:50:06.919
"Grislyland."

604
00:50:32.612 --> 00:50:34.363
A pleasant evening.

605
00:50:40.829 --> 00:50:42.288
(GRUNTING)

606
00:51:02.684 --> 00:51:04.852
(SCREAMING)

607
00:51:22.245 --> 00:51:23.996
