just resigned.

726
01:05:16.495 --> 01:05:18.997
I'm the new chairman
of the board.

727
01:05:20.541 --> 01:05:23.251
He always did
like that mausoleum.

728
01:05:23.336 --> 01:05:24.920
Put him in it.

729
